Proposed Solution:
Introduced the "Smart Plant Care System" as a comprehensive solution.
Outlined the three main components: sensors, Central Control System (CCS), and a user-friendly mobile app.
Explained sensor functionality in detecting environmental conditions (light, temperature, soil moisture).
Detailed automated responses, including watering, temperature adjustments, and supplementary light provision.
Emphasized the integration of artificial intelligence (AI) for real-time decision-making.
Described the user-friendly mobile app for remote monitoring and manual control
